{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-clarify-information-in-different-interactions/task-11","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Vežba 11","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Sada je vreme da predstavimo neke komade odeće na engleskom. U ovoj lekciji, Tom spominje dva komada koje obično nosite na gornjem delu tela.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">jacket</span> To je komad odeće koji nosiš preko druge odeće kako bi te ugrejao ili održao suvim. Obično ima duge rukave i zatvarače (zip) ili dugmad napred.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">shirt</span> je komad odeće koji pokriva gornji deo vašeg tela. Može imati kratke ili duge rukave i obično ima dugmiće ili kraka. Nosite ga ispod jakne ili samostalno. Ne pomešajte ga sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">T-shirt</span>, koji je obično opuštenija odeća i nema dugmiće.</p>\n</section>","instructions":"","explanation":null,"challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"English","superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","block":"learn-how-to-clarify-information-in-different-interactions","lang":"en-US","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-clarify-information-in-different-interactions/task-11"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>If you see her today, she's wearing a black and green BLANK and a beige BLANK.</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"jacket","feedback":"<p>Molimo vas da popunite ovo mesto sa komadom odeće koji nosite preko druge odeće kako biste se zagrejali ili zaštitili od hladnoće.</p>"},{"answer":"shirt","feedback":"<p>Molimo popunite ovo mesto komadom odeće koji pokriva gornji deo vašeg tela, obično ima dugmići, rukave i kraka jakne.</p>"}]},"inputType":null,"tests":[],"transcript":null,"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-center.png","characters":[{"character":"Tom","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.2},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"4.3-1.mp3","startTim